## Keyword Tiers

Keywords are organized into three tiers:
- **Tier 1 (Head)**: High volume (10K+ monthly searches), high competition — brand awareness, homepage, category pages
- **Tier 2 (Body)**: Moderate volume (1K–10K), moderate competition — subcategory pages, product listings, blog content
- **Tier 3 (Long-tail)**: Lower volume (<1K), lower competition, higher conversion — product pages, how-to guides, comparison articles

