## Content Strategy Framework

### Product Page Optimization
- **Title**: `[Weight Rating] [Brake Type] Trailer Axle [Lug Pattern] - [Brand]`
- **H1**: Match primary commercial keyword exactly
- **Meta description**: Include weight rating, brake type, price range, and "free shipping" or "in stock"
- **Body**: Include long-tail variants, specs table, compatibility notes, related products

### Category Page Optimization
- **Title**: `[Category] | Trailer Parts Unlimited`
- **H1**: Use Tier 1 keyword (e.g., "Trailer Axles", "Trailer Tires & Wheels")
- **Content**: 200–400 word intro with Tier 2 keywords woven in, filterable product grid, FAQ section

